  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for iproute2",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for iproute2 fixes the following issue\n\n- CVE-2024-58251: denial of service via terminal escape sequences (bsc#1254324).\n\nOther updates:\n\n- support display of bound but unconnected sockets (bsc#1204562)\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
